## 4. System Implementation Phases

### Phase 1: Foundation & Data Modeling (Non-AI)
*   Setup Next.js Frontend and FastAPI Backend.
*   Design and implement PostgreSQL database schema using SQLModel (Users, Tasks, Documents, Tickets).
*   Implement Google Auth & JWT Authentication.
*   Build simple CRUD APIs for the Onboarding Checklist and Admin Dashboard.

### Phase 2: Knowledge Base & RAG Setup
*   Setup ChromaDB/Qdrant.
*   Ingest college FAQs, hostel rules, and LMS guides into the Vector Database using Ollama embeddings.
*   Create a basic Chat Endpoint that queries this Vector DB.

### Phase 3: Multi-Agent Orchestration
*   Integrate LangGraph in the FastAPI backend.
*   Build the state graph and specialized agents (Task Agent, FAQ Agent, Routing Agent).
*   Give agents access to backend API functions (Tools).
*   Connect the Frontend Chat UI to this orchestrated backend.

### Phase 4: Workflows & Escalation
*   Implement Document Upload workflows with Tesseract and the Document Verification Agent.
*   Build the Escalation Agent to track unresolved queries and generate Helpdesk Tickets.

### Phase 5: Polish & Admin Tooling
*   Finalize Admin Dashboard analytics (completion rates, pending verifications).
*   UI/UX polish (glassmorphism, modern design aesthetics).

